Scott Forbes https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Scott_Forbes 0 Conrad Scott-Forbes (11 September 1920 – 25 February 1997), popularly known as Scott Forbes, was a film and television actor and screenwriter. In his later career as a screenwriter, he was credited as C. Scott Forbes.
